{
  "stem": "27340.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The boys would shave, and so on, and then on our beds we would find a white shirt and a clean pair of trousers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that shirt may have had somebody else's' name on them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, it was never your own shirt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was one that would fit you because the girls who were working in the laundry would obviously know your details, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What collar size you were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But since they were all open-neck shirts, in any case, it didn't matter if you had a size or two too large.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That didn't matter as long as it wasn't too small, because you have to button it up in the front.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So everything was commonly owned, and all the duties that were performed there were decided by the Vaad.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That means the commission.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Commission.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People were elected to those sort of things in exactly the same way as they were in the proper kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The only thing we didn't have on these training farms were we didn't have little children because people were single.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Although some, in fact, married, and there were one or two couples who joined us who were already married, but we had no children.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So other than that, we had this magnificent training farm of 350 acres or so, and after some time, I became the foreman of the farm gang.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Most of our people worked in local farms as laborers, and others worked as laborers, like I did, you know, even the farm foreman on the actual farm.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this was very convivial, wonderful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The thing that impressed me very much was the incredibly high moral standard, because there were verile men, and very young and very sort of beautiful girls there and so on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never had any hanky panky business.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
